<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Shipeasy · Ruby Entity Guide</title>
    <%#
      TODO: once shipeasy-sdk is installed, emit the i18n head tags here:
        <%= i18n_head_tags %>
    %>
    <%#
      We inline the stylesheet so the example boots with NO asset pipeline gem
      (propshaft/sprockets) and NO network calls. The source of truth is
      app/assets/stylesheets/guide.css.
    %>
    <style><%= Rails.root.join("app/assets/stylesheets/guide.css").read.html_safe %></style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <%= yield %>
  </body>
</html>
